"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-lifestyle-paris-2024-olympics-hot-olympians-best-looking-athletes-b1173769.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lifestyle  They are strong, they are fit, they are at the peak of their game\\u2026 Here are the most crush-worthy Olympians of Paris 2024  Olympians are hot.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.535051074680006e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a simple fact!\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are incredibly motivated, inconceivably healthy and quite literally at thetop of their game.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If we are throwing it back to the very beginning of this beloved competition, they are essentially the modern version of Greek gods.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9999995486515326, \"rank\": 4.5134884927576606e-07, \"text\": \"Greek gods\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they are well aware of it, too.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fewOlympianshave turned to OnlyFans in recent years to make some extra cash on the side of their sporting career.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As British diver Jack Laugher told The Telegraph recently: \\\"Obviously, I have got what people want.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9934145870766647, \"rank\": 0.006598751800137553, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jack Laugher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Laugher\"}, {\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Telegraph\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2639333464572175e-30, \"text\": \"The Telegraph\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Telegraph\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Telegraph\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will happily cash in on that.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a bit of a hustler and I want a bit more money if I can.\\\"\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But these Olympians come and they go.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to keep tabs on all the talented athletes, and by the time four years have passed, we have often forgotten who we were so captivated by at the last Olympic games, let alone the one before that, or before that.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember when we were all really into Chris Hoy?\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No?\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, it happened.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So who is the nextTom Daley?\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or Jessica Ennis?\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or Ryan Lochte?\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Lochte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the Paris Olympics 2024, here are 12 of the athletes we can not get enough of.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old French springboard diver had everyone's Speedos in a twist yesterday over the sight of him wearing his own tight trunks.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7456146424770037, \"rank\": 0.3335332050442011, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You think we'd all know how to be normal about swimmers in the Olympics competing in their little pants by now, but we just do not.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A home favourite and part-time model, Bouyer is hoping to take home the gold medal when he competes in the final of the men's synchronised 3m springboard on Friday.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bon chance, France!\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999988119405098, \"rank\": 1.1879042812630713e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This US gymnast may have been slightly overshadowed by the return of Simone Biles, but Sunisa \\\"Suni\\\" Lee is very much a star in her own right.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7355163737851036, \"rank\": 0.31503295372167267, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 2003, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa \\\"Suni\\\" Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2003, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa \\\"Suni\\\" Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee is the 10th most-decorated American female gymnast with multiple world championships and three Olympic medals under her belt.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9997326328088264, \"rank\": 0.00026743864372942046, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9980233454384407, \"rank\": 0.001980529524884983, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old is set to thrive at the Paris Olympics, despite being recently diagnosed with an incurable kidney disease.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's pretty hardcore.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And to top it all off, she recently became a campaign star for Kim Kardashian's underwear brand, Skims.\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Kardashian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another American standout is Ashleigh Johnson, the first Black woman to ever play on the US women's water polo team.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2450, \"end\": 2458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9980233454384407, \"rank\": 0.001980529524884983, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2471, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Johnson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ashleigh Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 2531, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7355163737851036, \"rank\": 0.31503295372167267, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nicknamed \\\"Ayay\\\", she's now a two-time Olympic champion, a Lacoste ambassador, and is widely considered one of the best goalkeepers in her field.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a height of 6 foot 1 and with a degree from Princeton, she's the real deal.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princeton_University\", \"score\": 0.7664450833110974, \"rank\": 0.3031317386892744, \"text\": \"Princeton\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princeton_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princeton_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This Italian backstroke champion has already gone viral for his looks at the Paris 2024 Olympics, namely for displaying his toned V-line abdominal muscles beneath his rather cropped Italia jersey as he lifted his arms in celebration on Monday 29 July.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2791, \"end\": 2798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9995012008612926, \"rank\": 0.0004435711902656448, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 2968, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vogue_Italia\", \"score\": 0.5872557259448814, \"rank\": 0.7028356741702005, \"text\": \"Italia\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vogue_Italia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vogue_Italia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, as one Australian news site put it, \\\"Wardrobe malfunction thrills Olympic fans\\\".\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3050, \"end\": 3060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999999272831728, \"rank\": 7.271702925447463e-08, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimmer was thrilled with his win, telling Italy's Rai television: \\\"Ever since I was a kid I knew I could win this medal and today is that day.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3171, \"end\": 3176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9972284810606026, \"rank\": 0.0027792216009789213, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"German relay runner Alica Schmidt is expected to leave many Olympics viewers a little winded when she appears on screen for the 4x400m relay.\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3273, \"end\": 3279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9574838510016133, \"rank\": 0.04438805907284945, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 3293, \"end\": 3306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\", \"score\": 0.999999999312422, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alica Schmidt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alica_Schmidt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old is a formidable runner, and a bit of a fashionista too, thanks to her Boss and Tiffany & Co ambassadorship positions.\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3510, \"end\": 3522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiffany_&_Co.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tiffany & Co\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiffany_&_Co.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiffany_&_Co.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a face that looks as if it was crafted by AI, you can expect her pristine ponytail and surprisingly stylish German running kits to be all over social media when she competes.\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3597, \"end\": 3599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9995399152175388, \"rank\": 0.0004602965581685238, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 3663, \"end\": 3669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9574838510016133, \"rank\": 0.04438805907284945, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This American sprinter has got it all: speed, style (see: his painted nails that said \\\"Icon\\\" at the opening ceremony) and buckets of confidence.\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3736, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9980233454384407, \"rank\": 0.001980529524884983, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"\\\"I do not feel the pressure because I am just having fun,\\\" Lyles told reporters of his mental state.\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All I gotta do is be me.\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I constantly tell kids all the time, 'Be yourself.'\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if people see me as being corny, shoot, I am corny.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But guess what?\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am winning while being corny.\\\"\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Jamaican athlete Kishane Thompson clocked a faster time this year, 26-year-old Lyles insists that he's the fastest man in the world right now.\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4174, \"end\": 4182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999998279609065, \"rank\": 1.7203946567215136e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 4199, \"end\": 4207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9700687171876756, \"rank\": 0.03085480675900559, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 4253, \"end\": 4258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.92743759131485, \"rank\": 0.07822629865388568, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only time will tell, as we wait to see him compete in the preliminary round on 3 August.\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The newly established GOAT of British women's running is Dina Asher-Smith.\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4429, \"end\": 4433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"score\": 0.7168567345956931, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GOAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\"}, {\"begin\": 4437, \"end\": 4444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9934145870766647, \"rank\": 0.006598751800137553, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 4464, \"end\": 4480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beloved by basically everyone, 28-year-old Asher Smith is currently Britain's fastest woman.\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4550, \"end\": 4557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9982865505182357, \"rank\": 0.001716390430195762, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brits can expect to see her winning smile, medal or not, on 2 August as the women's 100m gets underway.\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith herself has said she's confident of her medal-winning abilities, telling Sky News she's in an \\\"incredible place\\\" at the moment.\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4765, \"end\": 4773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"score\": 0.9999661109853967, \"rank\": 3.38901633953094e-05, \"text\": \"Sky News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me I want to get to Paris and put together a race that's worthy of getting on a podium,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4845, \"end\": 4850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.782064462727707e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who knew someone called Geraldina could be such a stunner!\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France is not letting us down as a host nation this year, with an abundance of gorgeous and talented athletes on the lineup.\", \"from\": 4984, \"to\": 5108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4984, \"end\": 4990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999988119405098, \"rank\": 1.1879042812630713e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes the so-called \\\"face of the games\\\" Leon Marchand, France's 22-year-old swimmer who's currently under the watchful eye of Michael Phelps's former coach, Bob \\u00adBowman.\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5172, \"end\": 5178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999988119405098, \"rank\": 1.1879042812630713e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5243, \"end\": 5257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.055393636694647e-84, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand has already broken an Olympic record and secured one gold medal at the Paris games with the 400m individual medley, but there is still more to come.\", \"from\": 5288, \"to\": 5445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5368, \"end\": 5373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.782064462727707e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Make like the French and yell \\\"Allez allez!\\\"\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"at your TV screen, maybe Marchand will hear you.\", \"from\": 5491, \"to\": 5539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5516, \"end\": 5524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999160762574809, \"rank\": 8.392017336898473e-05, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another member of the easy-on-the-eyes French contingent is Teddy Riner, the 35-year-oldjudoexpert (or \\\"judoka\\\") with eleven World Championships and three Olympic medals under his belt - which is 6th dan and black, FYI.\", \"from\": 5541, \"to\": 5760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5601, \"end\": 5612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teddy Riner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\"}, {\"begin\": 5756, \"end\": 5759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgin_Media_Two\", \"score\": 0.9999995839008036, \"rank\": 4.1609935066649936e-07, \"text\": \"FYI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgin_Media_Two\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgin_Media_Two\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a look at his judo skills, keep your eyes peeled on 2 August, when he's set to compete in the Men's +100kg round of 16.\", \"from\": 5762, \"to\": 5885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5866, \"end\": 5872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting_at_the_2008_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.7291834349237369, \"rank\": 0.37139703414164943, \"text\": \"+100kg\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting_at_the_2008_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Powerlifting_at_the_2008_Summer_Paralympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Riner is considered by many to be the greatest judoka in history, and unlike many of the other athletes on this list, he's not too young for us to feel weird about fancying him.\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 6063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hurrah!\", \"from\": 6064, \"to\": 6071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be a little ridiculous to go through a list of hot Olympians and not include a surfer, would not it?\", \"from\": 6073, \"to\": 6182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, Brazilian surfer Gabriel Medina is your man on the board for this Olympics - or off the board, it seems, as Medina's just gone viral for a \\\"perfect\\\" image of him levitating above the water, a metre away from his also-airborne board.\", \"from\": 6183, \"to\": 6421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6206, \"end\": 6220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 6297, \"end\": 6303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3206009054540644e-33, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, Medina's performance was near-perfect too, with the 30-year-old successfully taking on Kanoa Igarashi, the Japanese surfer who beat him at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 6423, \"to\": 6583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6433, \"end\": 6439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3206009054540644e-33, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 6520, \"end\": 6534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanoa_Igarashi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kanoa Igarashi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanoa_Igarashi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanoa_Igarashi\"}, {\"begin\": 6540, \"end\": 6548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9115264834937592, \"rank\": 0.09607104900698762, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 6572, \"end\": 6577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.654431938928232e-13, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that wave he was levitating over?\", \"from\": 6584, \"to\": 6621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That landed him a 9.90, the highest scoring wave in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 6622, \"to\": 6690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The yanks may be our rivals, but for good reason - they do produce some pretty amazing athletes.\", \"from\": 6692, \"to\": 6788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among them is sprinter Gabby Thomas.\", \"from\": 6789, \"to\": 6825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6812, \"end\": 6824, \"